"well as a refinement of its current types."
msgstr ""

#: src/0494-c_str-and-c_vec-stability.md:196
msgid ""
"The `from_vec_unchecked` function could do precisely 0 work instead of "
"always pushing a 0 at the end."
msgstr ""

